/h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/getwebmaxcom_wporg\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/caeb7ec0a040a9ebcca86b9f4087d92d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/caeb7ec0a040a9ebcca86b9f4087d92d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/getwebmaxcom_wporg\" class=\"reviewer-name\">getwebmax.com_wp.org</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">October 13, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I cannot believe that this plugin gets any sort of reviews above one star.  It is one of the worst plugins I have ever installed (paid versions of event tickets and event calendar).\n\nIt is difficult to customize, it is not friendly with themes, and there is no support.  \n\nI have wasted so much time trying to customize and get this to work with my theme without looking like the system was created as a grade-school effort.\n\nExtremely clunky doesn\'t even begin to describe this POS.\n\nAvoid at all costs!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plugin is more or less ok</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/malinose\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4e63621f42ee264d73e1163912cc39af?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4e63621f42ee264d73e1163912cc39af?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/malinose\" class=\"reviewer-name\">malinose</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">October 11, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I like the functionality of the plugin and it suits our needs totally \nbut the necessary addons are far far far too expensive which makes this plugin bad</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thobbes\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3d823ab9d93dc42a9f99e8090565e3ac?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3d823ab9d93dc42a9f99e8090565e3ac?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thobbes\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thobbes</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">October 8, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have been using this product in various projects for three customers for several years. In short: No customer was completly enthusiastic about the product. Only one customer still uses this software today. The main criticisms were the annual price for updates &amp; maintenance as well as the coding of the software (e.g. database/too many queries). The essential further development of the product and the support was also criticized. Based on the feedback from customers and users, I rate the free version of the product as good.\n\nBest wishes, Tom</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Date picker language</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trollheimendesign\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a2461c5db0a5e9405a78b9fb535a41a9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a2461c5db0a5e9405a78b9fb535a41a9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trollheimendesign\" class=\"reviewer-name\">trollheimendesign</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">October 4, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hello! :) \nThe date picker on the mounth view is on english, the rest is norwegian (my language), Is it any way to get the date picker norwegian to?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Not recommended</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/swinggraphics\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/65ad4c2bbbe1a282def2c76275938f51?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/65ad4c2bbbe1a282def2c76275938f51?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/swinggraphics\" class=\"reviewer-name\">swinggraphics</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">October 4, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">So they just changed their entire paid support system to one requiring a separate log in, but existing customers can\'t log in! The password reset does not work.\n\nThese guys don\'t seem to be able to do anything right, and I strongly advise clients and anyone else to seek another solution for calendars and ticketing. It would be great if it weren\'t for the bugs, odd limitations, gotchas, and continually frustrating support.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">PURCHASED PRODUCT - NO SUPPORT</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/darcyoordt\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eeedc3f8d70deaf4037a2f59f934b1b7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eeedc3f8d70deaf4037a2f59f934b1b7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/darcyoordt\" class=\"reviewer-name\">darcyoordt</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">October 4, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">You can only get support for this product if you log in to their forum and submit a ticket. However, the login and password DOESN\'T WORK!! I\'ve contacted them for TWO DAYS and they won\'t respond (except one response which changed my password to some god-awful long thing--but it wasn\'t a password issue). \n\nI\'ve tried everything I can to get a hold of them to get support for a product I paid $200 for. NOTHING!! I fixed my first issue--which was caused by their update--by uninstalling the update. But I have other issues that can\'t be resolved BECAUSE I CAN\'T GET THEIR SUPPORT AND THEY HAVE NO OTHER MEANS OF YOU CONTACTING THEM. \n\nStay away from them as they seem to have an issue with support</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Always loved this plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jwfoster2014\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40884653c93a2f7f3d454c2d11dfd0b5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40884653c93a2f7f3d454c2d11dfd0b5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jwfoster2014\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jwfoster2014</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 30, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve used this plugin MULTIPLE TIMES &amp; have ALWAYS loved it, just wish all the cool stuff wasn\'t extra $$</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Buggy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aamartines\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4f1c7048e7fe038bc810bf5b64fdbdd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4f1c7048e7fe038bc810bf5b64fdbdd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aamartines\" class=\"reviewer-name\">a.a.martines</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 28, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I regret buying the paid version of this plugin and the tickets extension. It\'s very buggy and asking for help on the support forum almost always results in \"we\'ll maybe fix it in a few months.\"\n\nSteer clear.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best Calendar plugin out there</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cookieweb\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dd687bbdf108b5e25431e6066e773f86?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dd687bbdf108b5e25431e6066e773f86?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cookieweb\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cookieweb</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 28, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been developing WordPress sites for 10 years and this is the best calendar plugin out there. The basic version is excellent, and having additional functionality available as premium add-ons is great for sites that need a bit more power.\n\nLove The Events Calendar - I\'m a big fan!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does exactly what I need</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ammolaze\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/07ede56c0b510797d1dabe7f60425f85?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/07ede56c0b510797d1dabe7f60425f85?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ammolaze\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ammolaze</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 26, 2018</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">No less th